snippet.title: Book of Demons Final Release Trailer
snippet.description:
Wishlist or download a FREE DEMO on Steam ➡ https://bit.ly/3tQRuGw

Discord ➡ http://discord.gg/bookofdemons
Twitter ➡ https://twitter.com/thingtrunk
Facebook ➡ https://facebook.com/ThingTrunk

Book of Demons is a Hack & Slash Deck-building hybrid in which YOU decide the length of quests. Wield magic cards instead of weapons and slay the armies of darkness in the dungeons below the Old Cathedral. Save the terror-stricken Paperverse from the clutches of the Archdemon himself!

Official website ➡ http://return2games.com
Dev blog ➡ http://thingtrunk.com
